properties.Name: ConsumerLineOfCreditStatus
properties.Description: The status of the line of credit as of the date for the associated reporting period.

Columns.Name: CreditGrantorId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Credit Grantor.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditAccountNumber
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a specific Line Of Credit provided to a Customer/Customer Account.

Columns.Name: ReportingDate
Columns.Description:
The date of the associated status.

Ex:

For the period Oct 1- Oct 31, the status of the credit card is detailed as of the date Oct 15.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditLimitAmount
Columns.Description: The period line of credit total amount.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditBalanceAmount
Columns.Description: The balance on the line of credit.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditTotalInterestPaid
Columns.Description: The total amount of interest paid to date upon the loan.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditTotalPrincipalPaid
Columns.Description: The total amount of principal paid to date upon the loan.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditLastPaymentDueDate
Columns.Description: The date of the last due payment.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditLastPaymentDueAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of the last payment due.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditLastPaymentMadeAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of the last payment made.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditLastPaymentMadeDate
Columns.Description: The date that the last payment was made.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditTotalOverduePaymentsAmount
Columns.Description: The total overdue payments as of the associated date.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditTotalDefaultPaymentsAmount
Columns.Description: The total amount of default payment as of the associated date.

Columns.Name: AccountStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Account Status.

Columns.Name: BillingCycleId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Billing Cycle.

Properties.Description: The status of the line of credit as of the date for the associated reporting period.
